    "The public TypeScript Chunk SDK has no tag 9 instruction builder.",
    "No current test directly exercises the client tree planner, generated_tree_fell_blocks, tag 9 settlement, a non-base cut, duplicate non-clicked coordinates, or the missing FoundationChunk check.",
